+        // stick can't scroll continuously via the event path; poll the live axis and nudge the window's
+        // text view directly (no Kotlin round-trip — the window is native). Same 60ms cadence as the
+        // DS-overlay scroll poll; 40px/step matches ScrollWindow::onKeyButtonPressed (arrow up/down).
+        {
